ers said that the agenda would be discussed at Monday\u2019s Standing Committee meeting.\n\nThe faction has decided to make the anti-government movement more systematic and strong.","title":"Prachanda-Nepal faction forms taskforce to decide future strategy - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/03/153885/","video":[]}
